{"tid":1306195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制CCTVB, 偏地開花, 連儂牆　都係維持民眾運動參與的糧食 以後其影響建議","createTime":"2019-07-11T05:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:31:10.000Z","uid":94771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1b9073bb11ebf9d4500d509b849a4301d5910f","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:24:12.000Z","msg":"抵制CCTVB<br />\n<br />\n每人都可以參與。最低成本來，只要你唔買落廣告的商戶貨物　已經係參與到<br />\n而且有成功感係維持運動的一種糧食來<br />\n<br />\n最重要係只要令民眾做到依種的習慣　紅媒的勢力就會弱好多<br />\n已經中立媒體會開始有廣告。<br />\n<br />\n偏地開花<br />\n<br />\n雖然有巴打話會失焦　但當你的遊行推動到人上街　人地自然會關注佐其他遊行活動<br />\n而且對抗建制派地區選舉係好有用<br />\n只要我地大主題成日提返五大訴求 其實反而係會吸引更多參加者參與五大訴求的運動<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆<br />\n好多人話無用,但其實係幾有用<br />\n如大埔咁 個個連儂牆幾乎已經變佐廣告 連唔關心政治的人都會去打卡<br />\n大埔百幾黑警搞2張poster 幾乎已經人人階知<br />\n連儂牆係有一定程度的廣告效應 放工經過都會見到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但我就唔建議守 應該係可以撕一貼十</span><br />\n<br />\n我認為依D活動對抗爭係有好處的 但我都認為唔好濫發 洗太平地咁出 <br />\n因為咁的確會有連登整體失焦問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n我有以下建議 :<br />\n<br />\n1. 做返個整合POST 大家將關於個個運動集中係個個POST會好好多 緊急事件除外 (其實用TG都得)<br />\n<br />\n2.希望連仔可以做個唔推POST的功能 就可以有唔同細POST 但唔會引致連登整體變佐經常要重新洗地,推POST問題<br />\n好多巴打話怕失焦其實係建基於一個問題 就係主流POST 全部唔見佐 潛佐水</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"05cda8aa63d925be376fa5583d09cd304787f3d5","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe80e3ee57458f9639a0cba5d01b1a5d3f899909","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5c7e461d8dd03beea14b3f7738ee0228c9f291","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"連濃場整合貼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1306205/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1306205/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"6e077b2c15e5251977ac45e7ac0003af01fe6e99","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf49b4d6cafb56da8d94109bdc110080f5e2435","tid":1306195,"uid":274658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"或者可以睇下admin可唔可以整個將整合好嘅post永久置頂？<br />\n咁樣下面可以繼續發其他消息嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e95168063eb1adb62c434121ac8f63d4bcc5c1","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6584e521cc2fa2c0b49e17ee591a19b605e4186","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faf49b4d6cafb56da8d94109bdc110080f5e2435","tid":1306195,"uid":274658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"或者可以睇下admin可唔可以整個將整合好嘅post永久置頂？<br />\n咁樣下面可以繼續發其他消息嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"希望連仔可以搞個投票功能<br />\n有1千票的POST可以置頂一段時間"},{"pid":"915ded20c14bbfc9f823962bd28ec34435ea2271","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1664f536f6c1617dd9a1148a83f4e69ca71c61de","tid":1306195,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d90cf600d9b4a93